      News story
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    GAD's role in pensions consultation
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">GAD has worked with the Northern Ireland Department of Justice by developing its response to the McCloud ruling, and provided wider pensions consultancy advice.</p>

  </div>
</div>

